    {
      "id": "sybil_15_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_15",
      "description": "Hey there! I'm selling my absolute pride and joy. This car is in stunning condition\u2014honestly, it looks and smells like it just left the showroom! I\u2019ve babied it since day one, and it drives like an absolute dream. If you're looking for a ride that\u2019s practically perfect and ready for a new adventure, you\u2019ve found it. I\u2019d love for it to go to someone who will appreciate it as much as I have!",
