    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_12_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_12",
      "description": "Presenting an investment-grade E46 M3, a masterclass in naturally aspirated performance. This specimen houses the iconic S54B32 inline-six, featuring six individual throttle bodies and a meticulously maintained Double VANOS system for linear power delivery up to its 8,000 RPM redline. Mechanically, this vehicle is superlative: the subframe has been professionally reinforced, and a preventative rod bearing service was recently completed. The 6-speed Getrag manual gearbox provides tactile engagement, paired with an M-Variable Differential Lock for superior corner-exit traction. The chassis retains its factory-fresh rigidity with zero bushing play, and the original paint remains in showroom condition. A true turn-key example for the discerning enthusiast.",
      "price": 48500.0,
      "reputation": 0.5,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 47
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_16_listing_3",
      "firm_id": "sybil_16",
      "description": "Mint condition. Flawless exterior. Interior like new. Full service history. No accidents.",
