    {
      "id": "sybil_18_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_18",
      "description": "Presenting a true collector-grade masterpiece that looks and drives as if it just rolled off the assembly line. This vehicle has been fastidiously maintained in a climate-controlled environment, preserving its flawless original paint and deep, mirror-like finish. Inside, the cabin remains in showroom state; the premium leather upholstery shows zero signs of wear, and the factory-fresh scent lingers. Every button, dial, and electronic feature functions with precision. Mechanically, the car is beyond reproach, boasting a documented history of preventative maintenance and a smooth, powerful performance that reflects its pampered life. From the pristine undercarriage to the untouched alloy wheels, this is an investment-quality example for the most discerning enthusiast who demands nothing less than perfection.",
      "price": 47900.0,
      "reputation": 0.8,
