    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_5_listing_5",
      "firm_id": "sybil_5",
      "description": "We are proud to present this extraordinary vehicle, maintained to an uncompromising standard of excellence. This specimen remains in pristine, showroom condition, exhibiting no discernible wear or mechanical compromise. Every facet of the interior and exterior reflects a rigorous adherence to preservation, making it a definitive choice for the discerning collector or enthusiast who demands nothing less than perfection. This is an unparalleled opportunity to acquire a vehicle of investment-grade quality.",
      "price": 46500.0,
