    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_19_listing_6",
      "firm_id": "sybil_19",
      "description": "Hey there! You honestly have to see this beauty in person to believe it. \ud83d\ude97\u2728 I\u2019ve taken absolute pride in keeping this car in pristine, showroom condition\u2014it\u2019s basically like it just rolled off the lot! It\u2019s been garage-kept, meticulously detailed, and runs like an absolute dream. If you\u2019re looking for something that\u2019s been loved and cared for with zero compromises, this is the one for you. Come say hi and take it for a spin; I promise you won\u2019t be disappointed!",
      "price": 44900.0,
