    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_13_listing_7",
      "firm_id": "sybil_13",
      "description": "Available is a collector-grade E92 M3, a masterclass in high-revving atmospheric engineering. At its heart lies the S65 4.0L V8, utilizing individual throttle bodies to achieve unparalleled throttle modulation and an 8,400 RPM redline. The chassis is uncompromised, featuring the factory-integrated Electronic Damper Control (EDC) and a Variable M Differential Lock for superior lateral dynamics. Weight distribution is optimized via the OEM carbon fiber reinforced plastic roof, significantly lowering the center of gravity for surgical turn-in. This vehicle presents in concours-level state, with the 6-speed manual gearbox and drivetrain exhibiting zero lash. A mechanically perfect example for the discerning purist.",
